280→                                            <p className="notif-content-sliced-text">{unreadNotification?.opinions?.opinion?.length > 100 ? unreadNotification?.opinions?.opinion?.substring(0, 100) + '...' : unreadNotification?.opinions?.opinion}</p>
281→                                        </div>
